python Steps for Devs
1. Install pyhton3 "https://www.python.org/downloads/" and make sure upon installation it is added to path.
2. Creating working environment by prompting the following on the terminal "python3 -m venv brahmmychat_venv"
then "source brahmmychat_venv/bin/activate" for os 
Or "python -m venv brahmmychat_venv" then ".\brahmmychat_venv\Scripts\Activate" for windows.
3. After successfully creating a virtual environment, prompt the ff. "pip install --upgrade pip" or ".\brahmmychat_venv\Scripts\python.exe -m pip install --upgrade pip" for windows
4. Next, "pip install -r requirements.txt"
5. streamlit run app.py
6. Download hugging face 
small: "https://huggingface.co/TheBloke/Mistral-7B-Instruct-v0.1-GGUF/blob/main/mistral-7b-instruct-v0.1.Q3_K_M.gguf"
large: "https://huggingface.co/TheBloke/Mistral-7B-Instruct-v0.1-GGUF/blob/main/mistral-7b-instruct-v0.1.Q5_K_M.gguf"
7. embeddings_path: "https://huggingface.co/BAAI/bge-large-en-v1.5"


